    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A small game made with love and humor. It takes only an hour to complete, but it is completely free. If you like it and it makes you smile, that's great!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is the game about?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kota, an elf cosplayer, arrives in a small village where she will help an old friend, teach magic to an orphan, take part in catching the legendary Sasalmon... well, just play and find everything out for yourself!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique mechanics!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As well as walking, your character can also RUN. And at some points in the game, a cute tiny chibi girl will follow you around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/17dca0826333e9f725b260c77a35575f.poster.avif?t=1732298434\" width=598 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/17dca0826333e9f725b260c77a35575f.webm?t=1732298434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/17dca0826333e9f725b260c77a35575f.mp4?t=1732298434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for hidden items in each level! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/3b3aa31ecab017bf5219fdde3e4f6b9e.poster.avif?t=1732298434\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/3b3aa31ecab017bf5219fdde3e4f6b9e.webm?t=1732298434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/3b3aa31ecab017bf5219fdde3e4f6b9e.mp4?t=1732298434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the many inhabitants of the village (sorry, I forgot to come up with a name for it)! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/a9bdf604ef8d7aeaa0d8941def4a2789.poster.avif?t=1732298434\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/a9bdf604ef8d7aeaa0d8941def4a2789.webm?t=1732298434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270680/extras/a9bdf604ef8d7aeaa0d8941def4a2789.mp4?t=1732298434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Okay, these mechanics aren't particularly unique, I guess. You might have seen some of them in other games...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NO AI-generated art or text</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every image and word in this game is handmade. Yes, they are not perfect. But you can be sure that hours of human effort have gone into them!</p>",
